Class DiscardFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.dinapolidinardo.view.DiscardFrame
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AlienDiscardFrame, HumanDiscardFrame

    public abstract class DiscardFrame
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that manages the creation and usage of the Frame initialized when user has to discard a card in game.
